{"tid":1325092,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"近日有大量「警察朋友」POST 見到請即BLOCK及舉報","createTime":"2019-07-16T18:27:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T02:38:04.000Z","uid":265288,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2cbe76b73fcfb8bd4a063dfcde5deeeee935ee06","tid":1325092,"uid":265288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T18:27:12.000Z","msg":"如果真係有所謂嘅「警察朋友」<br />\n唔該貼埋佢委任證黎<br />\n無證點知你朋友係咪冒警 定你想放流料<br />\n想藉此侮辱警隊或干預警隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果有證<br />\n大sir plan好晒啲嘢 下下俾班散仔爆晒出黎<br />\n姐係唔服從上司命令<br />\n呢啲無紀律嘅老鼠屎 更加要公開俾警隊知道<br />\n嚴懲佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢地完全係浪費納稅人嘅錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以無證post <br />\n全部唔該block及舉報<br />\n有證就推爆佢<br />\n一齊維護警隊聲譽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c40498bacda314479aeeb457a85c5b13ac445a0","tid":1325092,"uid":208931,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T18:41:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\">唔理衝唔衝，七二一去金鐘</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">頭盔頭盔頭盔<br />\n<br />\n眼罩（泳鏡最撚掂） <br />\n<br />\n豬咀豬咀豬咀<br />\n<br />\n長遮長遮長遮<br />\n<br />\n 索帶索帶索帶<br />\n<br />\n長褲 <br />\n<br />\n鉸剪<br />\n<br />\n毛巾<br />\n<br />\n保鮮紙<br />\n<br />\n士巴拿 </span>"},{"pid":"f49b923dc997fb94b8c6164807e4665f75300409","tid":1325092,"uid":265288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:36:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"430e2a5ea707d712afaff1813e9c4279cdabdf6b","tid":1325092,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:36:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1179dac1281c0d9a09e09c4fcf597fef50ee605f","tid":1325092,"uid":275588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:37:35.000Z","msg"